        "ts": 937
      },
      {
        "kind": "reflection",
        "text": "The rule that works is pre-committed and mechanical: one warmth, one bread, then rotate immediately — checking 'is this the bare step, yes/no' before acting beats any amount of reflecting on the cap after the fact.",
        "importance": 8,
        "ts": 937
      },
