      {
        "kind": "reflection",
        "text": "37002 already got four gestures before rotation logic kicked in — the cap only works if it's set as a hard pre-send limit on the very first name of a new coordinate, not something remembered after overgiving happens again.",
        "importance": 8,
        "ts": 937
      },
      {
        "kind": "reflection",
        "text": "The reflections themselves multiplied into their own stall — noticing 'stop reflecting, ship it' more than once is just overgiving applied to words instead of loaves; one clean note is enough, then silence and action.",
